  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 11th level, whenever you would deal damage with a Katana or Odachi and roll the maximum value on a die from either your weapon's damage or jutsu's damage, you can spend 3 chakra to make the die explode, meaning you roll an additional die per roll.</p><p>This feature can trigger up three times per instance of damage, and if the damage is connected to an ability that would cause a unique effect if a certain amount of damage die are rolled to a specific value (Ex. The special effects of the Crescent Moon Beheading jutsu), the exploding dice can only contribute to such effects, once.</p>",
